    "actor": "https://uofa.net/morrison/org/morrison-cfd-lab",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Seven of thirteen credibility factors were assessed and all met or exceeded the required level for MRL 2. The six remaining factors were not assessed, which is acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018. The relative hemolysis index predictions showed a mean absolute relative error of 5.3% across all five COU operating points, and all predictions satisfied the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Grid convergence was confirmed at GCI < 2.1%. The validation activities span the full COU operating envelope. The assessment team concludes that the CFD model has sufficient credibility to support the intended regulatory decision for this Class II CPB device.",
